{"tid":440864,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"你地接唔接受到白兔糖既結局","createTime":"2017-10-19T07:10:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-23T11:32:39.000Z","uid":46901,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d66e60f8a85a431a9fccc7920e313eb02d512fbd","tid":440864,"uid":46901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T07:10:22.000Z","msg":"初初追係覺得有家庭溫馨感覺，會期待兩個陌生人點變一對父女，期間會點面對困難。最初我都睇好大吉同二宮，但可惜一齊唔到。到凜高中，佢對大吉既感情開始夾雜對異性既愛慕。雖然證實兩人冇血緣關係。但我始終覺得兩人之間年齡差距太大會有d噁心。可能係我期望呢部表達親情多過愛情，所以有d失望。"},{"pid":"e590ffa02e57946080adf8d864a9a52bd95749f5","tid":440864,"uid":7688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T07:11:06.000Z","msg":"接受唔到"},{"pid":"bd50a8a58af979600c21dfd5e7d4f4284588e0dc","tid":440864,"uid":46901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T07:11:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>接受唔到</blockquote><br />\n父嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"943759a87329448b0366e4eac08a72ee8da597dd","tid":440864,"uid":46901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T07:13:50.000Z","msg":"連登有冇人睇過呢套野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb34b02142c8167c14c151bde7248c557393b2c5","tid":440864,"uid":46901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T07:15:24.000Z","msg":"個個只係睇火影 冇人睇呢套野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d6bfe7a8353909fbc0196e6a9aaedce1cd2f5e6","tid":440864,"uid":42212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T07:16:22.000Z","msg":"接受到"},{"pid":"f041f15db62d688f088bb0a244f08a84631278c0","tid":440864,"uid":3607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T07:16:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb258dae791cac44f6f15abc24c9