6a57eceb5d0d","tid":440864,"uid":46901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T07:49:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>接受到</blockquote><br />\n可唔可以講下點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n凜都冇當大吉係老豆, 當佢係照顧自己既人, 漫畫有一話凜仲係細過個陣都講咩大吉就大吉,唔肯跟大吉姓</blockquote><br />\n我都咁睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 凜對大吉從來都無親情</blockquote><br />\n可能我係果d世人眼光 年齡相差二十幾歲  同大吉同年齡既朋友都有凜咁大既小朋友 。係其他人眼中佢地係普通養父女既關係。佢地一齊之後面對既困難一直比以前多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"840243114e15c176c15e8e8cb0cb68639f9a0f4c","tid":440864,"uid":126985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T08:18:34.000Z","msg":"只睇過動畫<br />\n冇睇漫畫<br />\n當時聽到係鬼父結局接受唔到..."},{"pid":"a20d452bf1740785b5fd079851cd72d152905d4b","tid":440864,"uid":46389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T08:28:43.000Z","msg":"動畫肯定係佳作<br />\n漫畫結局垃撚圾"},{"pid":"661197b5d3a6bcc8401d90b7df2aeb71b49b20da","tid":440864,"uid":114217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T08:34:58.000Z","msg":"動畫無畫到大個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n漫畫接受唔到"},{"pid":"d36ac709765bf9af1e98d97bb8a27850f33e9931","tid":440864,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T08:51:24.000Z","msg":"用力抽插<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">冇睇</span></span>"},{"pid":"5c24681e5cf975901a12e1b101a2e3f5c662d84d","tid":440864,"uid":2023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T10:19:59.000Z","msg":"超接受唔到"},{"pid":"fe8581858bdc8b0a24775d085764f39cc0ae9b80","tid":440864,"uid":73356,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T11:32:39.000Z","msg":"如果佢用最普通既結局只會係一套好普通既作品 過2年冇人會提冇人會記得<br />\n正正係呢個結局成套野話題性多好多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}